org.sakaiproject.assignment.taggable.tool

Class DecoratedTaggingProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.assignment.taggable.tool.DecoratedTaggingProvider

  • public class DecoratedTaggingProvider
extends Object
    Wrapper around TaggingProvider for displaying a pageable/sortable list of tags for an activity or item. Since there may be multiple providers each with a list of tags displayed on a single page, this class enables each provider to maintain the page/sort state of its list separate from others.
    Author:
    The Sakai Foundation.
